content:
I am trying to fix a UCUM error that is appearing in the build - [java] ...resource Medication 0.309 169sec 1851MB
[java] UCUM eror: Error processing unit 'IU': The unit 'IU' is unknown' at position 0. I've tried what I believe to be valid UCUM units for International Units - IU and iU, but both of these give the same error. Does anyone know what it should be?
